name: futapocalypse 1.0
description:
This is a futa model built from hundreds of hours of research and training attempts. It is using fluffyrock-768-lion-low-lr-e38-offset-noise-e6 as a base. the base model this was trained on can be found in this discord server: https://discord.gg/furrydiffusion

CFG goes from 4-20+, sample steps go from 20-150 on Euler A with depreciating gains after 80 steps from my tests.

it's using E621 tags, not dabooru. you can get the autocomplete extension in the SD webui exstensions tab, then in the options you can switch to E621 for easy autocomplete.

futanari is the keyword, but gynomorph also works (furry art generation is possible with this tag).

i did my best to add all the good stuff, breast sizes go from flat chested -> small breasts -> medium breasts -> big breasts -> hyper breasts in that order.

ball size follows about the same as breast size.

it offers flaccid, erect, foreskin (retracted, partially retracted, unretracted).

it's not great at micropenis so watch out for that.

animal genitals work as well if your into that (canine/equine).

you're gonna need to use an artist name as a base, i use ricegnat for a more "waifu" look. but just about any artist on E621 with more than 50 images should work fine, you can even blend them by adding multiple artists!

noise offset was used, so you get great contrast!

the VAE i used was vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned, but you can experiment with others!

in the event of too much furry bleed through make sure to add "anthro, fur, tail" in the negative prompt or human in the prompt.

enjoy everyone!
